Author: justeatingair
Text: You'd think crying it out would help at least a little bit, it never does.   I feel like even if I end up a skinny legend I'm still going to look like some creature that could burn your eyes out if you dare to look twice.

Author: skeletonwannabe
Text: I feel you dude... my family’s going out to dinner tonight because my brother’s come to visit and I spent over an hour trying on outfits, looking in the mirror and ripping them off.   Now my room looks like a bomb site and I feel like crying... hehe love my life
